document: Web Development: Modern JavaScript frameworks, UI/UX design, and responsive layouts.
Introduction to AI: Core concepts and applications; practical labs and projects.
Operating Systems: Processes, memory, scheduling, and concurrency basics.
Cloud Computing: Virtualization, containerization, and distributed systems.
Database Systems: Relational modeling, SQL, indexing, and transactions.
Machine Learning: Supervised and unsupervised learning; model evaluation.
Software Architecture: Components, styles, and scalability principles.
Data Visualization: Interactive dashboards, storytelling with data, and visualization tools.
Network Fundamentals: IP addressing, switching, routing, and network troubleshooting.
Human-Computer Interaction: Interface evaluation, usability studies, and accessibility design.
